export enum FlexBoxDirection { /** * Items are placed top to bottom.
* Note: Corresponds to `column`. */ Column = 'Column', /** * Items are placed bottom to top.
* Note: Corresponds to `column-reverse`. */ ColumnReverse = 'ColumnReverse', /** * Items are placed left to right in `ltr` and right to left in `rtl`.
* Note: Corresponds to `row`. */ Row = 'Row', /** * Items are placed right to left in `ltr` and left to right in `rtl`.
* Note: Corresponds to `row-reverse`. */ RowReverse = 'RowReverse' }
